Quick Gun-Game map series.

GG_02 is the second map in my quick-map-making series.

The goal of this series is to produce as many completed maps as possible, mainly for experience.

The best will be re-textured, re-built and re-released.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Description: A medium sized map that provides many interesting lines of sight and cover spots.

Theme: height variation.

Size: Medium

Max Players: 44

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

At 9.8MB .bz2 is recommended.

Please tell me what you think.
